const ProductReducer = (state = initialState , action) => {

	switch(action.type){
		case 'NEW-STYLE' :
		return{
			...state,	
			style : 'auto'
		}
		case 'NEW-ACTIVE-SLIDE-PRODUCT' :
		if (action.text === 'New Products') {
			if (action.ActivePageNewProducts < 1) {action.ActivePageNewProducts = 1}
			if (action.ActivePageNewProducts > Math.ceil(state.NewProducts.length/6)) { console.log(Math.ceil(state.NewProducts.length/6)); action.ActivePageNewProducts = 1}
			return{
				...state,	
				ActivePageNewProducts:action.ActivePageNewProducts
			}
		}
		if (action.text === 'Top Products') {
			if (action.ActivePageNewProducts < 1) {action.ActivePageNewProducts = 1}
			if (action.ActivePageNewProducts > Math.ceil(state.NewProducts.length/3)) { action.ActivePageNewProducts = 1}
			return{
				...state,	
				ActivePageTopProducts:action.ActivePageNewProducts
			}
		}
		if (action.text === 'Sale Products') {
			if (action.ActivePageNewProducts < 1) {action.ActivePageNewProducts = 1}
			if (action.ActivePageNewProducts > Math.ceil(state.NewProducts.length/3)) { action.ActivePageNewProducts = 1}
			return{
				...state,	
				ActivePageSaleProducts:action.ActivePageNewProducts
			}
		}
		
		default:
			return state;	
	} 	
}

export const NewStyle = () => {
	return {
		type:'NEW-STYLE'
	}
}
export const NewActiveSlideProduct = (ActivePageNewProducts,text) =>{
	return {
		type:'NEW-ACTIVE-SLIDE-PRODUCT',
		ActivePageNewProducts,
		text
	}
}


export default ProductReducer;
